"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-zharnel-hughes-team-gb-100m-paris-2024-b2492820.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Exclusive interview: The Team GB star and British record holder in the 100m and 200m tells Jack Rathborn about plans to take down world champion Noah Lyles in Paris and time away from family during his development in Jamaica  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 547, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 307, \"end\": 311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"score\": 0.9999999739238777, \"rank\": 2.130933422280742e-08, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\"}, {\"begin\": 361, \"end\": 371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 375, \"end\": 380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.46786430474185e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 433, \"end\": 440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.47195413081663e-20, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Zharnel Hughesremembers the sacrifices and the pain.\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 624, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was hunched over after another gruelling repetition on a Kingston track under the blazing sun when the legendaryUsain Boltcried out, urging the teenager to get back to work.\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 801, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 685, \"end\": 693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingston_upon_Thames\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.73810461672504e-16, \"text\": \"Kingston\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingston_upon_Thames\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingston_upon_Thames\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, many years later, the Great Britain star,a bronze medalist in the 100mat last year's Budapest World Championships, appreciates his journey.\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 947, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 830, \"end\": 843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.8055165456973752, \"rank\": 0.24143111227596376, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 893, \"end\": 901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999999296483135, \"rank\": 7.035183337876919e-08, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The agony of leaving his mother and three brothers behind in Anguilla eventually subsided.\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 1039, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1010, \"end\": 1018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anguilla\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0341621059970049e-15, \"text\": \"Anguilla\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anguilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anguilla\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hughes represents Team GB because the International Olympic Committee does not recognise Anguilla, which is a British overseas territory.\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1058, \"end\": 1065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4599067313016302e-13, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1078, \"end\": 1109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1150, \"end\": 1176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Overseas_Territories\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British overseas territory\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Overseas_Territories\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Overseas_Territories\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, Hughes became driven by the buzz from rubbing shoulders with track royalty such as Bolt and an opportunity to achieve greatness.\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1315, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1187, \"end\": 1193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.999999987830961, \"rank\": 7.904753992924234e-09, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I moved to Jamaica at 16 years old.\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1358, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1334, \"end\": 1341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.47195413081663e-20, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I left my family, we are really close.\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1397, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I remember leaving my mum at the airport and that final goodbye, you are a little fish into a huge ocean.\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1503, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's scary,\\\" Hughes tellsTheIndependentinside a Shoreditch coffee shop ahead of a busy year leading towards theParis Olympics.\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1630, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1552, \"end\": 1562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shoreditch\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.067416812927936e-19, \"text\": \"Shoreditch\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shoreditch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shoreditch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But you have to grow up, you have no choice.\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1677, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was a junior, stepping into a professional environment and it was so strict.\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1756, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had to work hard.\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1776, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watching Usain at training was just incredible.\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1824, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was looking up to him, studying him on YouTube every day.\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1866, \"end\": 1873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"score\": 0.9999999999899956, \"rank\": 1.0140036473590193e-11, \"text\": \"YouTube\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was motivation.\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1905, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I saw him dying on the track.\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 1937, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If he's working hard and already the world's fastest man, what do I have to do?\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 2017, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just tried to compete.\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2042, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I remember he said to my coach: 'Who's this little boy?'\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2099, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I came home and shouted: 'Mummy, I ran with Usain in training!'\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2165, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have a very good relationship, he will give me a fist pump and he congratulated me after Budapest.\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2267, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2258, \"end\": 2266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999999296483135, \"rank\": 7.035183337876919e-08, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I still look up to him.\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have to respect the man, he changed the sport.\\\"\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2343, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hughes has gathered immense momentum after a breakthrough last year, banishing his Tokyo Olympics demons after squandering an opportunity in the 100m due to a false start.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2345, \"end\": 2351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.999999987830961, \"rank\": 7.904753992924234e-09, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After a series of blazing runs last summer, he is now the British record holder over the 100m (9.83 seconds) and 200m (19.73 seconds).\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Indeed, lightning struck twice to snatch two 30-year-old records from \\u200b\\u200bBritish icons Linford Christie and John Regis.\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2738, \"end\": 2754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linford_Christie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Linford Christie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linford_Christie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linford_Christie\"}, {\"begin\": 2759, \"end\": 2769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Regis_(athlete)\", \"score\": 0.9999872251534899, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"John Regis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Regis_(athlete)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Regis_(athlete)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Given that 100m time is identical to Noah Lyles' gold-medal winning performance in Budapest, it would be easy to allow his mind to wander, knowing a similar performance in Paris could clinch sporting immortality on one of the greatest stages in sport.\", \"from\": 2772, \"to\": 3023, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2809, \"end\": 2819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 2855, \"end\": 2863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999999296483135, \"rank\": 7.035183337876919e-08, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}, {\"begin\": 2944, \"end\": 2949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.46786430474185e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are keen to go even lower, I will not tell you the exact times, but I intend to smash last year, I am even stronger this year,\\\" Hughes says.\", \"from\": 3025, \"to\": 3169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3157, \"end\": 3163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.999999987830961, \"rank\": 7.904753992924234e-09, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not study Noah, but he's a 200m specialist like myself, we have very good top-end speed.\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3265, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3187, \"end\": 3191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Bennet\", \"score\": 0.851699197584744, \"rank\": 0.1713685737185266, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Bennet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Bennet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If I can keep that and work on my first bit of the race, that's where I lose a bit of time, because of my height, I am trying to get my steps as quick as possible, while maintaining my positioning to get to my top speed.\", \"from\": 3266, \"to\": 3486, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not think about Noah, I need to set myself up properly and turn on the afterburners in the second half of the race.\\\"\", \"from\": 3487, \"to\": 3608, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3508, \"end\": 3512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Bennet\", \"score\": 0.851699197584744, \"rank\": 0.1713685737185266, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Bennet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Bennet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hughes might not mix with Lyles much away from the track, but his presence is inescapable, namely inside the cauldron of the call room moments before the gun is fired, which often proves pivotal before the first stride.\", \"from\": 3610, \"to\": 3829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3636, \"end\": 3641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.994731104950951, \"rank\": 0.005286619253847008, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not need to be close to my rivals,\\\" Hughes explains.\", \"from\": 3831, \"to\": 3889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3873, \"end\": 3879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.999999987830961, \"rank\": 7.904753992924234e-09, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are super competitive.\", \"from\": 3890, \"to\": 3916, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our egos will not allow it, we can clash.\", \"from\": 3917, \"to\": 3958, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The tension in there, you can cut it with a knife, it's tough.\", \"from\": 3960, \"to\": 4023, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"People are screwed up, slapping their thighs, staring at you.\", \"from\": 4024, \"to\": 4085, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's all mind games.\", \"from\": 4086, \"to\": 4106, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has settled races in the past, most definitely, and the start line too.\", \"from\": 4108, \"to\": 4183, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You hear people making strange sounds, trying to get into your head.\", \"from\": 4184, \"to\": 4252, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Americans, screaming 'USA, baby!'\", \"from\": 4253, \"to\": 4290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4253, \"end\": 4266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.796213727784639e-22, \"text\": \"The Americans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 4279, \"end\": 4282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999947090146, \"rank\": 4.991171059152269e-09, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has shown me that sport is 90 per cent mental and the rest is physical.\", \"from\": 4291, \"to\": 4365, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you can not manage the pressure, the 100m really can break you.\\\"\", \"from\": 4366, \"to\": 4433, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After succumbing to the pressure in Tokyo, Hughes now embraces the spotlight and the added glare from the Netflix cameras that follow his every move around London during an intense day of media duties with new sponsor GetPRO.\", \"from\": 4435, \"to\": 4660, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4471, \"end\": 4476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8886866444759093, \"rank\": 0.12525602383135195, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 4478, \"end\": 4484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.999999987830961, \"rank\": 7.904753992924234e-09, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}, {\"begin\": 4541, \"end\": 4548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.2617869847199783e-12, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}, {\"begin\": 4591, \"end\": 4597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.483818808210521e-12, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Track and field is preparing for its Drive to Survive treatment this summer.\", \"from\": 4661, \"to\": 4737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4698, \"end\": 4703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Drive\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8459716054086074e-28, \"text\": \"Drive\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Drive\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Drive\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But despite a chill from a gloomy London and redemption in the 100m, a fire still burns inside Hughes.\", \"from\": 4739, \"to\": 4841, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4773, \"end\": 4779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.483818808210521e-12, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 4834, \"end\": 4840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.999999987830961, \"rank\": 7.904753992924234e-09, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 4x100m silver medal in Tokyo was cruelly taken away after CJ Ujah tested positive for two banned substances, but that heartache now unites a group and gives purpose to Hughes beyond personal glory.\", \"from\": 4842, \"to\": 5043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4869, \"end\": 4874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8886866444759093, \"rank\": 0.12525602383135195, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 4904, \"end\": 4911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Ujah\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CJ Ujah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Ujah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Ujah\"}, {\"begin\": 5014, \"end\": 5020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.999999987830961, \"rank\": 7.904753992924234e-09, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What happened, it hampered us, but it has made us more determined,\\\" Hughes admits.\", \"from\": 5045, \"to\": 5128, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Going forward we have another opportunity.\", \"from\": 5129, \"to\": 5172, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are more motivated, it's like we want revenge.\", \"from\": 5173, \"to\": 5222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We take lots of pride in relays.\", \"from\": 5224, \"to\": 5257, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have shifted that narrative.\", \"from\": 5258, \"to\": 5289, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is unity.\", \"from\": 5290, \"to\": 5305, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We take time to get the practice done.\", \"from\": 5306, \"to\": 5344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Warm weather training, we get our relay camps in, the details have helped us to fine tune everything.\", \"from\": 5345, \"to\": 5446, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is good chemistry.\", \"from\": 5448, \"to\": 5473, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are evolving, too.\", \"from\": 5474, \"to\": 5495, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Reece [Prescod] is running nine seconds, Eugene [Amo-Dadzie] is running nine seconds, Jeremiah [Azu] is running 10.0.\", \"from\": 5496, \"to\": 5613, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5582, \"end\": 5590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremiah\", \"score\": 0.999999163442121, \"rank\": 8.365438016374654e-07, \"text\": \"Jeremiah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremiah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremiah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have versatility now.\", \"from\": 5614, \"to\": 5638, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is great energy and good vibes.\", \"from\": 5640, \"to\": 5678, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Especially Richard Kilty, he gets you pumped up.\", \"from\": 5679, \"to\": 5727, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are still one unit.\", \"from\": 5728, \"to\": 5750, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is love and respect there.\\\"\", \"from\": 5751, \"to\": 5784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"GetPRO is the Official Yoghurt Partner of Team GB for the Paris 2024 Olympic Games  Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 5786, \"to\": 6100, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5921, \"end\": 5932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.217827606523494e-26, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"